thread.title_full: Family Stickers reviewed by D D FISHER

author: D D FISHER
title: D D FISHER
text:
Great items.
Would have got 5* if post wasn't so expensive & on top I had to pay additional import tax, if the packing had of been flat maybe & value under £20 then this wouldn't have cost me £11 on top of the $8:95 postage! Bit disappointing for a couple of car stickers!
Anyway girlfriend likes them on back of car!
